tions to different model skeletons.</li>\n  <li>Successfully adapted models by adjusting position, quaternion values of joints, and animation weights.</li>\n  <li>Implemented additive or blending animation effects, such as idle, walk, and jump sequences.</li>\n  <li>Developed features to export Threejs scenes to both static images and GIF captures.</li>\n  <li>Referenced Threejs documentation and examples to guide development processes:\n    <ul>\n      <li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://threejs.org/examples/#webgl_animation_skinning_blending\">Skinning Blending Example</a></li>\n      <li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://threejs.org/docs/index.html?q=animation#api/en/animation/AnimationAction.setEffectiveWeight\">Animation Action Effective Weight Documentation</a></li>\n      <li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://threejs.org/examples/#webgl_animation_skinning_additive_blending\">Additive Blending Example</a></li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n<p><i>Note: unfortunately, the real application images are confidential and cannot be shared.</i></p>\n<figure style=\"display: block; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center\">\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 543px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 140.10416666666669%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"clip tracks data array\" title=\"clip tracks data array\" src=\"/static/b9c87660552aa02deec752bfb87c3a13/29579/clip_tracks_data_array.png\" srcset=\"/static/b9c87660552aa02deec752bfb87c3a13/8514f/clip_tracks_data_array.png 192w,\n/static/b9c87660552aa02deec752bfb87c3a13/804b2/clip_tracks_data_array.png 384w,\n/static/b9c87660552aa02deec752bfb87c3a13/29579/clip_tracks_data_array.png 543w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 543px) 100v